&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2958380202474691&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xDPwdsfsa9ho5XlkU3tJD73ibLO98n47W0ib68V8gCDsmwcbuMML5uuxLPALeibQ2jDDhawvWOWs6m4Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;889&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;一位同学妈妈的反应也很有趣：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;男生在和妈妈说完我爱你之后：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5596508244422891&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xDPwdsfsa9ho5XlkU3tJD73DylK9s74Ftic8XwGGsFiaqzjCicNvbsEC72QGmdH4zeHsDh7MTiaRfhtjA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1031&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;妈妈回应道：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.28336557059961315&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xDPwdsfsa9ho5XlkU3tJD736drRmcIfa9qAJibhmhLiagamFQgglp7IaIJUibviaLBVUVIhdAdwM5HfVg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1034&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;并调侃道：&lt;/p&gt;

